00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:24.320
[Amit Varma]: is Auronavo Sinha, who is no stranger to lovers of Bengali literature. Auronavo has translated

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:29.800
[Amit Varma]: more than 50 books from Bengali to English and has introduced authors such as Asha Poornadevi,

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:35.040
[Amit Varma]: Shankar, Bankimchandra Chattopadhyay, Sharadandu Bondopadhyay, Sunil Gangopadhyay, Bonofool

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:42.200
[Amit Varma]: Buddhadeb Bose, Banuranjan Byapari and Noborun Bhattacharya to a wider English reading audience.

